            <title><![CDATA[Indie JRPGs showcase Indie Quest 2025 set for May 29]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/indie-jrpgs-showcase-indie-quest-2025-set-for-may-29</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/indie-jrpgs-showcase-indie-quest-2025-set-for-may-29.1193037/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/indie-jrpgs-showcase-indie-quest-2025-set-for-may-29<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
        </ul>

    
    <p><span>Includes "must-see world premiere from a critically-acclaimed studio."</span>
      </p></div><div><p>YouTube channel The Gaming Shelf has announced Indie <a title="Platforms > Quest [138 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/meta/quest">Quest 2</a>025, a new showcase spotlighting independently developed <a title="Genres > JRPG [1,644 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg/jrpg">JRPGs</a>. It will premiere on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@TheGamingShelf" target="_blank">YouTube</a> on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20250529T2300" target="_blank">May 29 at 4:00 p.m. PT / 7:00 p.m. ET</a>. <span id="more-965689"></span></p><p>The broadcast will feature over 40 exclusive game trailers, a “must-see world premiere from a critically-acclaimed studio,” and popular YouTube creators introducing each game.</p><p>“From tactical throwbacks to inventive turn-based experiments, Indie Quest celebrates the full spectrum of what modern Indie JRPGs can be,” reads the announcement. “Whether you’re a fan of pixel art nostalgia or boundary-pushing new mechanics, this showcase promises something for every <a title="Genres > RPG [17,261 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg">RPG</a> enthusiast—and some new surprises along the way.”</p><p>Watch a teaser trailer below.</p><h2><span>Teaser Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Introducing Indie Quest: A New Showcase for JRPG Fans!" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4S-xXQTH_DA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
        </div></div>]]></content:encoded>
