            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-the-soulless-army-the-principles-of-raidou-episode-1-trailer<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>The world of the Taisho era capital and ally demons.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > ATLUS [2,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/atlus">ATLUS</a> has released a new trailer for <em><a title="Games > RAIDOU Remastered: The Mystery of the Soulless Army [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-the-soulless-army">RAIDOU Remastered: The Mystery of the Soulless Army</a></em>, introducing the world of the 20th year of the Taisho era, the time in which Raidou lives, as well as the “Demons allies” who fight alongside him. <span id="more-965665"></span></p><p><em>RAIDOU Remastered: The Mystery of the Soulless Army</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,489 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,209 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [140 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,006 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [13,978 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,098 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,153 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2288350/RAIDOU_Remastered_The_Mystery_of_the_Soulless_Army/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> on June 19. Read more about the game <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/03/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-the-soulless-army-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-switch-and-pc">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/04/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-the-soulless-army-details-more-characters-demons-and-progression-systems">here</a>, and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-the-soulless-army-details-more-characters-locations-facilities-replayability-elements-and-dlc">here</a>.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>The Principles of RAIDOU: The World of the Taisho Era Capital and Ally Demons</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="THE PRINCIPLES of RAIDOU｜The World of the Taisho Era Capital and Ally Demons" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HrbscpZE5qI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
